&lt;h3 id=&quot;some-query-operation&quot;&gt;Some Query operation&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# Select all rows that have an age column greater than 30&lt;/span&gt;
