&lt;p&gt;Machine learning is about extracting knowledge from data. It is a research field at the intersection of &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;statistics&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;artificial inteligence&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;computer science&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;installation&quot;&gt;Installation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;System configuration we tested on is  &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;ubuntu 16.04&lt;/code&gt; with &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;python3&lt;/code&gt;. For easy installation of packages in python, we recommend installing &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;pip&lt;/code&gt; - a package managment tool for python.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;sudo apt-get install python3-pip&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we will be using &lt;a href=&quot;http://scikit-learn.org/stable/index.html&quot;&gt;scikitlearn&lt;/a&gt; an open source machine learning library. Since &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;scikitlearn&lt;/code&gt; has dependencies on other packages, we also need to install them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Python 2.7&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip install numpy scipy matplotlib ipython scikit-learn pandas&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Python 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip3 install numpy scipy matplotlib ipython scikit-learn pandas&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;jupyter-notebook&quot;&gt;Jupyter Notebook&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For interactive python, you can use &lt;a href=&quot;http://jupyter.org/&quot;&gt;jupyter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Install Jupyter&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip install jupyter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To start &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Jupyter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;jupyter notebook&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">Introduction</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Lesson-3: A First Application: Classifying Iris Species</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/lesson/2017/09/15/Lesson-3-First-Application.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Lesson-3: A First Application: Classifying Iris Species" /><published>2017-09-15T12:31:56+05:30</published><updated>2017-09-15T12:31:56+05:30</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/lesson/2017/09/15/Lesson-3-First-Application</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/lesson/2017/09/15/Lesson-3-First-Application.html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;introduction&quot;&gt;Introduction&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Machine learning is about extracting knowledge from data. It is a research field at the intersection of &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;statistics&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;artificial inteligence&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;computer science&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;installation&quot;&gt;Installation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;System configuration we tested on is  &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;ubuntu 16.04&lt;/code&gt; with &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;python3&lt;/code&gt;. For easy installation of packages in python, we recommend installing &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;pip&lt;/code&gt; - a package managment tool for python.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;sudo apt-get install python3-pip&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we will be using &lt;a href=&quot;http://scikit-learn.org/stable/index.html&quot;&gt;scikitlearn&lt;/a&gt; an open source machine learning library. Since &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;scikitlearn&lt;/code&gt; has dependencies on other packages, we also need to install them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Python 2.7&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip install numpy scipy matplotlib ipython scikit-learn pandas&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Python 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip3 install numpy scipy matplotlib ipython scikit-learn pandas&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;jupyter-notebook&quot;&gt;Jupyter Notebook&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For interactive python, you can use &lt;a href=&quot;http://jupyter.org/&quot;&gt;jupyter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Install Jupyter&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pip install jupyter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To start &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Jupyter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;jupyter notebook&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">Introduction</summary></entry></feed>